    - title: The Coming Destruction
      content: "Pack your bags and prepare to leave;\n\tthe siege is about to begin.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "For this is what the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> says:\n\t\u201CSuddenly,
        I will fling out\n\tall you who live in this land.\n\tI will pour great troubles
        upon you,\n\tand at last you will feel my anger.\u201D  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "My wound is severe,\n\tand my grief is great.\n\tMy sickness is incurable,\n\tbut
        I must bear it.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "My home is gone,\n\tand no one is left to help me rebuild it.\n\tMy
        children have been taken away,\n\tand I will never see them again.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The shepherds of my people have lost their senses.\n\tThey no longer
        seek wisdom from the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t.\n\tTherefore, they
        fail completely,\n\tand their flocks are scattered.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Listen! Hear the terrifying roar of great armies\n\tas they roll
        down from the north.\n\tThe towns of Judah will be destroyed\n\tand become
        a haunt for jackals.  "
      comments: []
    - title: "Jeremiah\u2019s Prayer"
      content: "I know, <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t, that our lives are not our
        own.\n\tWe are not able to plan our own course.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "So correct me, <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>\n\t, but please be gentle.\n\tDo
        not correct me in anger, for I would die.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Pour out your wrath on the nations that refuse to acknowledge you\u2014\n\ton
        the peoples that do not call upon your name.\n\tFor they have devoured your
        people Israel[COMMENT[0]];\n\tthey have devoured and consumed them,\n\tmaking
        the land a desolate wilderness."
      comments:
